html
  body
    .col-lg-9
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading Maintenance Mode
        | &#x9;
        .panel-body
          form
            .checkbox
              label
                input(type='checkbox', data-field='maintenanceMode')
                |  
                strong Maintenance Mode
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            p.help-block
              | When the forum is in maintenance mode, all requests will be redirected to a static holding page.
              | Administrators are exempt from this redirection, and are able to access the site normally.
            | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
            .form-group
              label(for='maintenanceModeMessage') Maintenance Message
              | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;
              textarea.form-control(data-field='maintenanceModeMessage')
      .panel.panel-default
        .panel-heading Domain Settings
        | &#x9;
        .panel-body
          form
            .form-group
              label(for='allow-from-uri') Set ALLOW-FROM to Place NodeBB in an iFrame:
